{"tid":1769094,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Fifa Pro Club 老牌球隊招人","createTime":"2019-12-04T14:56:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T02:11:48.000Z","uid":4039,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4a43a00cb52be25c7f51a5b54a5ff8b6fff76d2e","tid":1769094,"uid":4039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T14:56:47.000Z","msg":"球隊由多年前創立，打過大大小小既比賽。但生活逼人，球隊經歷過多次解散，就退左落黎。<br />\n<br />\n現時香港暴政橫行，民不聊生，多個fifa 比賽接連暫停及關閉。現希望可以尋找一班志同道合既隊友，o係忙上加忙既生活中抖抖氣，打下fifa。<br />\n<br />\n招募位置：任何位置<br />\n開波時間：視乎當日情況，大約 10:30pm-1:30am<br />\n主要以陣地戰為主，可長可短，配合為先，有個人技術更佳。<br />\n<br />\n現有數名隊員，誠邀各位置球員加入<br />\n<br />\n有意者請tg：eidllaopop<br />\n會參加比賽，願香港早日光復！<br />\n<br />\n謝絕藍絲撐警傻鳩"},{"pid":"ef63cd9c4220b3733bde9aca57e8d98dc3cc950a","tid":1769094,"uid":4039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T06:50:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a2a6c9581c3cd797ba7ef80f738ca6b47569ca6a","tid":1769094,"uid":202831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T14:07:19.000Z","msg":"pc?"},{"pid":"9640af689e290af099933901d4cd13a2929c2ecb","tid":1769094,"uid":4039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2a6c9581c3cd797ba7ef80f738ca6b47569ca6a","tid":1769094,"uid":202831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T14:07:19.000Z","msg":"pc?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T05:21:15.000Z","msg":"ps4"},{"pid":"6c9735857bc9b22e2fb379d75add2c1634212c12","tid":1769094,"uid":4039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T14:45:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fe7f85e667803c0613598200d1d170c696485bc1","tid":1769094,"uid":4039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T02:11:48.000Z","msg":"push"}]}